description: Imports the COM interfaces from an IDL file for use with .NET. Can handle c-style arrays and OLECHAR pointers.
releaseNotes:
Changes since version 2.0.0

Changed:
- switched to .NET Standard 2.0

Removed:
- removed TypeLib attribute support in code generation
- removed deprecated binary serialization

See full changelog at https://github.com/sillsdev/IdlImporter/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md
